INSERT INTO `contents` VALUES ('about-member-4--description_en', '<br />\nJoseba Ega&ntilde;a is the founder of Kendu and Kool. In 2000, he created the communication agency Medio 10, dedicated to the retail sector. The company worked together with 0.99 Studio, a design studio also founded by him, specialized in the design of promotional elements and visual merchandising.<br />\n<br />\nIn view of the opportunity to create a more diverse and dynamic offer for the point of sale, Joseba founded Kendu in 2004. This new company was born to develop and produce a pioneering graphic support of the time, which allowed the easy exchange of visuals printed on textile support, a system that he registered as Smartframe. In 2012, Kendu absorbed Grupo M10 within its commercial activity, and began its most multidisciplinary and international journey. Currently Kendu company employs more than 180 people in its offices around the world.<br />\n<br />\nIn 2019, in view of the new retail scenario and the importance of partnerships between brands, professionals and companies, Joseba founded Kool; the first hub specialized in retail. Thus, in 2020, it opened the doors of its first headquarters in Madrid, and has an ambitious international expansion plan to create a network of hubs interconnected by the main cities of the world', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `contents` VALUES ('about-member-4--description_es', 'Es el fundador de Kendu y Kool; un emprendedor nato. En el a&ntilde;o 2000 cre&oacute; la agencia de comunicaci&oacute;n Medio 10, dedicada al sector retail. La empresa trabaj&oacute; junto con 0,99 Studio, estudio de dise&ntilde;o tambi&eacute;n fundado por &eacute;l, especializado en el dise&ntilde;o de elementos promocionales y visual merchandising.<br />\n<br />\nEn el 2004 fund&oacute; Kendu para desarrollar y producir un soporte gr&aacute;fico pionero de la &eacute;poca, que permit&iacute;a el f&aacute;cil intercambio de los visuales impresos en soporte textil, sistema que registr&oacute; como Smartframe. En 2012, Kendu absorbi&oacute; Grupo M10 dentro de su actividad comercial, y comenz&oacute; su andadura m&aacute;s multidisciplinar e internacional. Actualmente Kendu emplea a m&aacute;s de 180 personas en sus sedes de todo el mundo.<br />\n<br />\nEn vista del nuevo escenario del retail y la importancia de las colaboraciones entre marcas, profesionales y empresas, Joseba funda Kool; el primer hub especializado en retail. En el 2020, abri&oacute; las puertas de su sede en Madrid, y cuenta con un plan de expansi&oacute;n internacional para crear una red de hub interconectados en las principales ciudades del mundo.', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
